tasks.summary:
Пакет internal/ingress/sse: Handler struct с TokenValidator/KVStore/Subscription consumer-side интерфейсами, NewHandler с component logger. Handle() → http.HandlerFunc: JWT extraction из ?token= query param → ValidateToken → http.Flusher check → http.ResponseController.SetWriteDeadline(time.Time{}) (disable server WriteTimeout для long-lived SSE) → SSE headers (Content-Type: text/event-stream, Cache-Control: no-cache, Connection: keep-alive, X-Accel-Buffering: no) → 200 OK → generate connID (UUID v4) → registerConnection в Redis (key sse:conn:{org}:{user}:{conn}, TTL=heartbeat×3, JSON record) → Subscribe на Redis Pub/Sub channel sse:broadcast:{org_id} с buffered events channel (cap 64, non-blocking send, drop on full + WARN log) → writeComment("connected") → eventLoop. eventLoop select: events→extractEventType+writeSSEEvent, heartbeat→writeHeartbeat+refreshConnection, maxAge→connection_expired event+return, ctx.Done()→return. SSE wire format: writeSSEEvent с multiline data support (strings.Split на 
, каждая строка с data: prefix — SSE spec compliance), writeHeartbeat (:ping

), writeComment (: text

). extractEventType с sanitizeEventType (strip 
/ — SSE injection prevention). isExpiredError (jwt.ErrTokenExpired). Connection lifecycle: registerConnection/refreshConnection (kv.Set с TTL), unregisterConnection (detached 2s context для cleanup после ctx cancel). Adapter: KVStoreAdapter bridges *kvstore.Client → sse.KVStore interface (Subscribe returns Subscription interface vs concrete type). Wiring: Deps.SSEHandler в server.go, registerRoutes с nil-guard fallback на sseStub. Code review fixes: M-01 http.ResponseController.SetWriteDeadline (WriteTimeout не убивает SSE), M-02 multiline data (strings.Split), M-03 sanitizeEventType (injection prevention). 35 тестов (+ 14 sub-tests): auth (3 — missing/invalid/expired token), flusher (1), SSE headers (1), connected comment (1), connection lifecycle (2 — register/unregister), event delivery (4 — status_update/comparison/missing type/invalid JSON), heartbeat (2 — ping + refresh TTL), max connection age (1), client disconnect (1), write error (1), backpressure (1), subscribe failure (1), Redis failures (2 — register/unregister), channel (1), subscription close (1), extractEventType (10 subtests), sanitizeEventType (6 subtests), multiline data (1), isExpiredError (4 subtests), key/channel format (2), constructor (1), interface checks (3). Нет новых зависимостей (jwt, uuid, chi уже в go.mod).
